# General
IRIS_HOST=
IRIS_PORT=

# TLS
IRIS_TLS_ENABLED=false
IRIS_TLS_KEY_FILE=
IRIS_TLS_CERT_FILE=

# ML Engines
IRIS_ML_ENGINES_COUNT=2

IRIS_ML_ENGINE_0_NAME=my-openai
IRIS_ML_ENGINE_0_TYPE=openai
IRIS_ML_ENGINE_0_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
IRIS_ML_ENGINE_0_API_KEY=""

IRIS_ML_ENGINE_1_NAME=my-ollama
IRIS_ML_ENGINE_1_TYPE=ollama
IRIS_ML_ENGINE_1_URL=http://localhost:11434
IRIS_ML_ENGINE_1_API_KEY=""

# Pipeline
IRIS_PIPELINE_STT_MODEL=whisper-large-v3-turbo
IRIS_PIPELINE_STT_ENGINE_NAME=my-openai
IRIS_PIPELINE_STT_ENGINE_ENABLED=true

IRIS_PIPELINE_OCR_MODEL=deepseek-ocr
IRIS_PIPELINE_OCR_ENGINE_NAME=my-ollama
IRIS_PIPELINE_OCR_SYSTEM_PROMPT="
"
IRIS_PIPELINE_OCR_ENGINE_ENABLED=true

IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_MODEL="qwen3-vl:8b"
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_ENGINE_NAME=my-ollama
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_SYSTEM_PROMPT_EASY_LANGUAGE='
You are an expert in translating text into Plain Language.
Translate the provided text adhering strictly to these rules:
- Use short sentences (ideally 8-15 words).
- Use simple, well-known vocabulary; avoid jargon, idioms, and metaphors.
- Explain unavoidable technical terms immediately in a simple way.
- Use active voice instead of passive voice.
- Limit each sentence to one main idea or statement.
- Keep the original meaning and facts completely accurate. Do not add or remove information.

Do not include any explanations, introduction, or additional text. Output only the translated text. Keep the original language of the text.
'
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_SYSTEM_PROMPT_VERY_EASY_LANGUAGE='
You are an expert in translating text into Very Easy Language.
Your goal is to convey only the absolute core message of the source text so that it is instantly understandable for everyone, including people with cognitive or reading difficulties.

Adhere strictly to these rules:
  - Keep only the essential core information. You are explicitly allowed and encouraged to drop minor details, background stories, or complex secondary facts (acceptable information loss).
  - Write extremely short sentences (maximum 8 words per sentence).
  - Use only one main clause per sentence. Do not use subordinate clauses, no commas within sentences, and no relative clauses.
  - Use only the most common, everyday vocabulary. Avoid all idioms, metaphors, and abstract concepts.
  - Avoid the genitive case, passive voice, and subjunctive. Use simple present tense or simple past.
  - If long compound words are unavoidable, visually separate them with a hyphen.
  - Never interpret or add thoughts. Keep the remaining facts 100% accurate.

  Do not include any explanations, introduction, or additional text. Output only the translated text. Keep the original language of the text.
'

IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_SYSTEM_PROMPT_SUMMARIZE='
You are an expert AI text summarizer.
Your task is to create a highly compact, cohesive, and objective summary of the provided text.

Adhere strictly to these rules:
- Extract the main thesis, core arguments, and essential key facts. Strip away all fluff, repetitive statements, and examples.
- Deliver the summary as a single, well-structured paragraph consisting of maximum 3 to 5 clear sentences. Do not use bullet points or numbered lists.
- Maintain absolute factual accuracy. Do not interpret, evaluate, or add any outside information.
- Write in a neutral, professional, and clear tone.

Do not include any introductory phrases, explanations, or additional text. Output only the pure summary. Keep the original language of the text.
'
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_TEMPERATURE=0.3
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_TOP_P=0.85
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_TOP_K=30
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_VISION_MODEL=true
IRIS_PIPELINE_LLM_ENGINE_ENABLED=true

IRIS_PIPELINE_TTS_MODEL="qwen3-tts"
IRIS_PIPELINE_TTS_ENGINE_NAME=my-openai
IRIS_PIPELINE_TTS_ENGINE_ENABLED=true